  steps:
  - id: welcome
    text: 'Welcome to Revival of Spirit Stone!

      Tutorial: Please read the subtitles
      on the screen!'
    holdDuration: 5
    typewriterSpeed: 25
    keysToShow: 250000000f0000002100000012000000
  - id: jump
    text: Space button lets you jump through tricky platforms
    holdDuration: 5
    typewriterSpeed: 25
    keysToShow: 01000000
  - id: pickup
    text: Use your E key to pick-up "Living stones"
    holdDuration: 5
    typewriterSpeed: 25
    keysToShow: 13000000
  - id: throw
    text: Holding Left mouse click lets you throw the stones to the point you desire.
    holdDuration: 5
    typewriterSpeed: 25
    keysToShow: 37000000
  - id: aim
    text: You see the bridge? Try aiming towards the next island and let the stone
      do its magic! If you miss, you can use R key to retrieve your stones.
    holdDuration: 5
    typewriterSpeed: 25
    keysToShow: 3700000020000000
  - id: bridge
    text: Congratulation on crossing the bridge! Now, see what secrets does arc hide!
    holdDuration: 5
    typewriterSpeed: 25
    keysToShow: 
